commit_message:
Leverage _mm_lddqu_si128 for sse3 and above arch

Fixes https://github.com/xtensor-stack/xsimd/issues/556

issues.title: [sse3] Leverage _mm_lddqu_si128 for unaligned load
issues.body:
`_mm_lddqu_si128` may perform better than `_mm_loadu_si128` for unaligned load.
https://software.intel.com/sites/landingpage/IntrinsicsGuide/#text=_mm_lddqu&expand=4195,4195

In an simd program I'm doing. Performance improves from 5.49GB/s to 5.88GB/s when replacing `_mm_loadu_si128` with `_mm_lddqu_si128`.
